  "title": "Sales Engineer (Training Provided)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Medical Devices Manufacturing Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $4500 - $5500 + Allowance + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Boon Lay</strong></li><li><strong>Working day: Monday to Friday</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 8.30am to 5.30pm</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Identify sales opportunities and develop new accounts through market research and trends</li><li>Proactively follow-up on assigned sales leads generated at market specific trade shows or web</li><li>Prepare and submit quotations/proposals/project schedule</li><li>Ensure customer orders are tracked accordingly</li><li>Manage and grow existing accounts to ensure continuous growth</li><li>Expand market share with existing and new customers</li><li>Enhance value-added selling approach</li><li>Provide quality after-sales support services</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess minimum Diploma/Degree in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent with minimum 1-2 years relevant experience</li><li>Prior experience in engineering or medical related field would be an added advantage</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
